  "_meta": {
    "version": 21,
    "info": {
      "name": "Clear the Kitchen",
      "image": "/i/noto-emoji/emoji_u1f408_200d_2b1b.svg",
      "rules": "",
      "bgg": "https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgame/172507/mmm",
      "year": "2015",
      "mode": "coop",
      "time": "15",
      "attribution": "Board layout by ArnoldSmith86. Released to public domain under CC0.\n\nImages are Noto Emoji, Material Symbols and Game-icons.net. See About for details.",
      "lastUpdate": 1774004246854,
      "skill": "",
      "description": "A cooperative dice-placement push-your-luck game where you try to finish food patterns efficiently before the cat advances too far.",
      "similarImage": "",
      "similarName": "Mmm!",
      "similarDesigner": "Reiner Knizia",
      "similarAwards": "2016 Kinderspiel des Jahres Nominee\n2016 JUGuinho Children Game of the Year Finalist\n2015 Spiel der Spiele Game of the Year Winner",
      "ruleText": "<h2 data-start=\"219\" data-end=\"234\">🎯 Objective</h2><p data-start=\"235\" data-end=\"322\">Work together to <strong data-start=\"252\" data-end=\"295\">remove all food from the pantry (board)</strong> before the cat reaches it.</p><ul data-start=\"324\" data-end=\"453\"><li data-start=\"324\" data-end=\"372\"><p data-start=\"326\" data-end=\"372\">✅ Win: All food spaces are covered with mice</p></li><li data-start=\"373\" data-end=\"453\"><p data-start=\"375\" data-end=\"453\">❌ Lose: The cat reaches the pantry first</p></li></ul><h2 data-start=\"460\" data-end=\"475\"><br></h2><h2 data-start=\"460\" data-end=\"475\">🧩 Core Idea</h2><ul data-start=\"476\" data-end=\"730\"><li data-start=\"476\" data-end=\"551\"><p data-start=\"478\" data-end=\"551\">The board shows <strong data-start=\"494\" data-end=\"533\">food items made of multiple squares</strong> (2-5 spaces each)</p></li><li data-start=\"552\" data-end=\"626\"><p data-start=\"554\" data-end=\"626\">You <strong data-start=\"558\" data-end=\"624\">“eat” food by fully covering all its squares with mouse tokens</strong></p></li><li data-start=\"627\" data-end=\"730\"><p data-start=\"629\" data-end=\"730\">You do this using <strong data-start=\"647\" data-end=\"665\">dice placement</strong> (not movement, not memory)</p></li></ul><h2 data-start=\"737\" data-end=\"775\"><br></h2><h2 data-start=\"737\" data-end=\"775\">🎲 Turn Structure</h2><h3 data-start=\"777\" data-end=\"795\">1. Roll 3 dice</h3><p data-start=\"796\" data-end=\"811\">Each die shows:</p><ul data-start=\"812\" data-end=\"934\"><li data-start=\"812\" data-end=\"867\"><p data-start=\"814\" data-end=\"867\">🧀 food types (bread, fish, cheese, carrot, cucumber)</p></li><li data-start=\"812\" data-end=\"867\"><p data-start=\"814\" data-end=\"867\">❌ or an “X” (no placement)</p></li></ul><h3 data-start=\"941\" data-end=\"970\">2. Place at least ONE die</h3><ul data-start=\"971\" data-end=\"1125\"><li data-start=\"971\" data-end=\"1034\"><p data-start=\"973\" data-end=\"1034\">You <strong data-start=\"977\" data-end=\"1008\">must place at least one die</strong> on a matching food square</p></li><li data-start=\"1035\" data-end=\"1125\"><p data-start=\"1037\" data-end=\"1125\">The symbol must match the food type on the board</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"1037\" data-end=\"1125\">You may:</p><ul data-start=\"1136\" data-end=\"1242\"><li data-start=\"1136\" data-end=\"1174\"><p data-start=\"1138\" data-end=\"1174\">Place more dice immediately<br data-start=\"1165\" data-end=\"1168\">\n<strong data-start=\"1168\" data-end=\"1174\">or</strong></p></li><li data-start=\"1175\" data-end=\"1242\"><p data-start=\"1177\" data-end=\"1242\">Reroll remaining dice (but only if you placed at least one first)</p></li></ul><h3 data-start=\"1249\" data-end=\"1289\">3. Continue or stop (push-your-luck)</h3><p data-start=\"1290\" data-end=\"1301\">You repeat:</p><ul data-start=\"1302\" data-end=\"1345\"><li data-start=\"1302\" data-end=\"1345\"><p data-start=\"1304\" data-end=\"1345\">Place ≥1 die → optionally reroll the rest</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"1304\" data-end=\"1345\">Until:</p><ul data-start=\"1354\" data-end=\"1441\"><li data-start=\"1354\" data-end=\"1378\"><p data-start=\"1356\" data-end=\"1378\">You stop voluntarily</p></li><li data-start=\"1379\" data-end=\"1401\"><p data-start=\"1381\" data-end=\"1401\">You place all dice</p></li><li data-start=\"1402\" data-end=\"1441\"><p data-start=\"1404\" data-end=\"1441\">OR you <strong data-start=\"1411\" data-end=\"1441\">can’t place any die → bust</strong></p></li></ul><h2 data-start=\"1448\" data-end=\"1478\"><br></h2><h2 data-start=\"1448\" data-end=\"1478\">💥 Busting</h2><p data-start=\"1479\" data-end=\"1491\">You bust if:</p><ul data-start=\"1492\" data-end=\"1542\"><li data-start=\"1492\" data-end=\"1542\"><p data-start=\"1494\" data-end=\"1542\">You roll dice that <strong data-start=\"1513\" data-end=\"1542\">cannot be placed anywhere</strong></p></li></ul><p data-start=\"1544\" data-end=\"1559\">➡️ If you bust:</p><ul data-start=\"1560\" data-end=\"1648\"><li data-start=\"1560\" data-end=\"1648\"><p data-start=\"1562\" data-end=\"1648\">You place <strong data-start=\"1572\" data-end=\"1608\">no mouse tokens at all this turn</strong></p></li></ul><h2 data-start=\"1655\" data-end=\"1684\"><br></h2><h2 data-start=\"1655\" data-end=\"1684\">🐭 End of Turn: Place Mice</h2><p data-start=\"1685\" data-end=\"1709\">If you did <strong data-start=\"1696\" data-end=\"1708\">not bust</strong>:</p><ul data-start=\"1710\" data-end=\"1773\"><li data-start=\"1710\" data-end=\"1773\"><p data-start=\"1712\" data-end=\"1773\">Replace each placed die with a <strong data-start=\"1743\" data-end=\"1758\">mouse token</strong> on that square</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"1775\" data-end=\"1810\">This gradually fills up food items.</p><h2 data-start=\"1817\" data-end=\"1839\"><br></h2><h2 data-start=\"1817\" data-end=\"1839\">🍽️ Completing Food</h2><ul data-start=\"1840\" data-end=\"1914\"><li data-start=\"1840\" data-end=\"1914\"><p data-start=\"1842\" data-end=\"1914\">When <strong data-start=\"1847\" data-end=\"1889\">all squares of a food item are covered</strong>, it is “eaten” (secured)</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"1916\" data-end=\"1944\">👉 This matters for the cat…</p><h2 data-start=\"1951\" data-end=\"1989\"><br></h2><h2 data-start=\"1951\" data-end=\"1989\">🐱 Cat Movement</h2>The cat moves <strong data-start=\"2005\" data-end=\"2022\">1 step closer</strong> if:\n<ul data-start=\"2028\" data-end=\"2148\"><li data-start=\"2028\" data-end=\"2048\"><p data-start=\"2030\" data-end=\"2048\">You <strong data-start=\"2034\" data-end=\"2042\">bust</strong>, OR</p></li><li data-start=\"2049\" data-end=\"2148\"><p data-start=\"2051\" data-end=\"2148\">You <strong data-start=\"2055\" data-end=\"2108\">fail to complete at least one food item that turn</strong></p></li></ul><p data-start=\"2051\" data-end=\"2148\"><strong data-start=\"2055\" data-end=\"2108\"></strong>👉 So even a “good” turn can still advance the cat if you didn’t finish food.</p><h2 data-start=\"2450\" data-end=\"2476\"><br></h2><h2 data-start=\"2450\" data-end=\"2476\">⚖️ Important Subtleties</h2><ul data-start=\"2477\" data-end=\"2802\"><li data-start=\"2477\" data-end=\"2580\"><p data-start=\"2479\" data-end=\"2580\">Players decide <strong data-start=\"2494\" data-end=\"2506\">together</strong> where dice go (fully cooperative)</p></li><li data-start=\"2581\" data-end=\"2688\"><p data-start=\"2583\" data-end=\"2688\">Food items have <strong data-start=\"2599\" data-end=\"2618\">different sizes</strong>, making some harder to finish</p></li><li data-start=\"2689\" data-end=\"2802\"><p data-start=\"2691\" data-end=\"2715\">There’s a <strong data-start=\"2701\" data-end=\"2714\">hard mode</strong>:</p><ul data-start=\"2718\" data-end=\"2802\"><li data-start=\"2718\" data-end=\"2802\"><p data-start=\"2720\" data-end=\"2802\">All dice must go in the same row or column</p></li></ul></li></ul>",
